        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Despite initial family reservations, Wichai and Anong find comfort in each other's company. Anong, a high-society lady, is sought after by many, and her family wants to find her a good match. Wichai, a passionate lawyer, is tasked with screening potential husbands for her. As he redefines what it means to be worthy, Anong realizes no one is more suitable than Wichai. However, he only sees her as a sister-in-law. Determined, Anong\n\ntries to win his heart, despite the slim odds.",
